{"id": "work_64bc3798-d01d-5b38-a0d4-33bd63818984", "title": "Randomized Benchmarking and Process Tomography for Gate Errors in a Solid-State Qubit", "sources": [{"source": "dtic", "id": "pub.1002126584"}], "last_updated": "2026-03-09T19:36:29.879537", "abstract": "We present measurements of single-qubit gate errors for a superconducting qubit. Results from quantum process tomography and randomized benchmarking are compared with gate errors obtained from a double pi pulse experiment. Randomized benchmarking reveals a minimum average gate error of 1.1+/-0.3% and a simple exponential dependence of fidelity on the number of gates. It shows that the limits on gate fidelity are primarily imposed by qubit decoherence, in agreement with theory.", "publication_date": "2009-03-05", "doi": "10.1103/physrevlett.102.090502", "url": "https://dtic.dimensions.ai/details/publication/pub.1002126584?and_facet_researcher=ur.015527265674.84", "citation_count": 0, "authors": [{"author_id": "author_a9877bfb-d7df-5d77-8b9d-194867128b30", "org_id": "org_cf6683eb-25ad-50fe-a19d-855f6e3e86df"}, {"author_id": "author_346a830e-67fe-5ca2-9afe-fc59ec3e813d", "org_id": "org_8b8083c2-32dd-5898-b6b9-b48bbf50c649"}, {"author_id": "author_ee827f15-7b96-5e6a-8360-933fdfa95ff4", "org_id": "org_07df67cf-a37e-5f14-97c4-b043bf14ae48"}, {"author_id": "author_d7dabd2b-cb1f-5727-810b-f51248afae22", "org_id": "org_cf6683eb-25ad-50fe-a19d-855f6e3e86df"}, {"author_id": "author_c758827b-3356-5691-aab4-b8395042bbf8", "org_id": "org_cf6683eb-25ad-50fe-a19d-855f6e3e86df"}, {"author_id": "author_14dc1e6b-eb21-5940-96fc-7d8b84783e30", "org_id": "org_cf6683eb-25ad-50fe-a19d-855f6e3e86df"}, {"author_id": "author_161bc9f4-7392-5c2b-9b2f-a41ce9b126d2", "org_id": "org_cf6683eb-25ad-50fe-a19d-855f6e3e86df"}, {"author_id": "author_d2b8b900-5488-5f87-ab9d-06fb3b0ff50b", "org_id": "org_cf6683eb-25ad-50fe-a19d-855f6e3e86df"}, {"author_id": "author_05d4b046-8319-56cd-a216-425dff836a4f", "org_id": "org_cf6683eb-25ad-50fe-a19d-85